/// Task-level value mapping. Each AI task (Behavior_Category) maps to a defensible work archetype and task-generic success metrics (Usage / KPI Impact / Workflow Automation). No inferred scenario attribution. Source: Microsoft Frontier Firm success-metric framework (2025), applied at task level.
